## Workflow

1. **Read TDD** - Extract backend design section
2. **Create Entity** - Sequelize entity với decorators
3. **Create DTOs** - All request/response DTOs first
4. **Create/Update Service** - Add method signatures, extend CrudService if needed
5. **Create/Update Controller** - Add endpoints
6. **Create/Update Providers** - Register Sequelize entity if needed
7. **Create/Update Module** - Register everything
8. **Register in AppModule** - If new module
9. **Check Lints** - Ensure no errors
10. **Update Task Checklist** - Mark tasks as `✅ (Scaffolded)`

